</p>
<ul class="org-ul">
<li>Acorn UK do not get all their funding from member dues, instead 40% of the funds are from external organisations including the Rosa Luxemberg Institute</li>
<li>Acorn National suppressed a motion that had been put forward by the Leeds (?) branch which would have made it necessary to disclose these sources.</li>
</ul>

