<div id="outline-container-org4cbec58" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="org4cbec58"><span class="todo TODO">TODO</span> big red flag: following in the footsteps of Acorn US?</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-org4cbec58">
<p>
Im a member of ACORN UK and am concerned that the union we are trying to copy ACORN US which seems to have had issues. I am particularly spooked by the fact that Acorn UK's National level leadership seem to be very close to Wade Rithke, the former head organiser of ACORN US and current head organiser of ACORN International. The issues with Wade Rithke
</p>

<p>
What happened to Acorn US, and is Acorn US similar in anyway to Acorn UK?
</p>
</div>
