<div id="outline-container-org24f2769" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="org24f2769"><span class="todo TODO">TODO</span> Issues not directly related to National</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-org24f2769">
<p>
There are myriad issues that are not apparently caused by ACORN's inherent structure or from ACORN National seemingly sabotaging things.
As a general rule, the issues I speak about will apply to my local branch, and I may have a hazy understanding that these issues are shared across the entire organisation (or at least this is my assumption, which I am happy for people to challenge).
</p>
</div>

