<div id="outline-container-orgde8ef57" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="orgde8ef57"><span class="todo TODO">TODO</span> Summary</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-orgde8ef57">
<p>
Acorn UK has so many issues. The branch I'm in is a major city (in top 20 most populated cities in the UK) but we handle maybe one or two member defense cases a month. We have been unable to grow membership at all in the past few years. Active members dwindle.
</p>
</div>
</div>
