<ul class="org-ul">
<li>great article that goes into far more depth with problems with Wade Rithke.</li>
<li>it pins the root cause of many of the issues that we are facing as an organisation in the paid/volunteer split in Acorn, which I think is probably true.</li>
<li>would be good if American comrades who experienced this stuff could provide their account of Wade, see if we can substantiate and further develop thinking in this piece.</li>
</ul></li>
